    <!--
        Plugin logo, converted from the SVG sources in Images/Logo*.svg (320x298 viewBox).
        All four variants share the same seven geometries; only the fills differ:
          - PlayAch.Image.Logo       multicolor gradients (Images/Logo.svg)
          - PlayAch.Image.LogoDark   dark navy gradient   (Images/Logo_Dark.svg)
          - PlayAch.Image.LogoGold   gold gradient        (Images/Logo_Gold.svg)
          - PlayAch.Image.LogoWhite  flat white           (Images/Logo_White.svg)
        PlayAch.Geometry.Logo is the combined monochrome silhouette for uses that supply their
        own brush (e.g. the sidebar/top panel icons, which inherit Playnite's foreground).
        Gradient Start/EndPoints are in geometry (SVG userSpaceOnUse) coordinates, hence
        MappingMode="Absolute".
    -->

